o 用 Intel HAXM 嚟加速 emulate 個 Application，所以比用 AMD CPU 快好多，不過做嘢通常都係 build 落真機試，用咩 CPU 都無咩所謂。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nC++ / GPU dev 唔熟，答唔到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db07e4923b898a7b0606c8873d8b5dc8f262bdc","tid":283991,"uid":58894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"唔該晒咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我狗衝ryzen了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dc43f09ce84f5cbeae69a2fb6d2a480e57721c","tid":283991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該晒咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我狗衝ryzen了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記往到時唔好比sales 哄兩哄買左i5-7600<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd19989b7911e39c2a111c6f0b6f4bc7c7bd9d6d","tid":283991,"uid":58894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2002ef4ce82caea02881a6071892dc47b674090","tid":283991,"uid":58894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"黃金ryzen 5 1600都冇貨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左新高登問都要成set買先得<br />\n但係佢又冇條Ram<br />\n佢介紹geil evo for2a 2400hz <br />\n<br />\n有冇人介紹鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869b6ca083de7a36e0df09fe80b087fd2371cfdb","tid":283991,"uid":62675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃金ryzen 5 1600都冇貨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去左新高登問都要成set買先得<br />\n但係佢又冇條Ram<br />\n佢介紹geil evo for2a 2400hz <br />\n<br />\n有冇人介紹鋪